Name: Meow Express
About the game: You are a cat on a robot vacuum cleaner. Which means you are bus driver in the cat world! Dodge obstacles, pop innocent kids' baloons, dash through buildings to collect your fellow cat pussengers and deliver them to the promised pillow land! - Hover around the course - Dash through obstacles - Upgrade your flying robot vacuum cleaner - Collect different cat pussengers - Like literally, collect your pussengers Meow Express is a jam-game made within a couple of days. It has memes, smol easter eggs, engaging and enraging gameplay, hand drawn art, meowy melodies, pun-full cat city names and more!
